    <statement><p>Factor the given polynomial.</p>
<p><m>8r+8=</m> <fillin characters="19" name="AnSwEr0001"/></p>
</statement>
    <answer>
      <p>
        <m>8\mathopen{}\left(r+1\right)</m>
      </p>
    </answer>
    <solution><p>The greatest common factor is <m>8</m>, so we can factor the polynomial as follows:</p>
<p><m>8r+8={8\mathopen{}\left(r+1\right)}</m></p>
</solution>
